ass="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="65" height="21" style="display: none; top: 68px !important; left: 44px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-679023" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false">If you're a parent with a preteen or tween who's starting to experience those inevitable hormonal changes, breakouts, and shifts in their skin; then this is blog is for you.&nbsp;<div><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px;"><br></span></div><div><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px;">As we all know, growing up means both mental and physical transformations, and guess what? Our skin doesn't want to miss out on the fun either! In this edition of SkinTalks, get ready to take a look into the world of tween skincare with a straightforward starter routine.</span></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1681731921397" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681731921397" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1681731921345" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681731921345" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="8+4" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-sm-8 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921352" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1681731921352"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 12.5px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 26px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-5051" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">1. Pyunkang Yul - Deep Cleansing Oil</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921395" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1681731921395" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">If you've got a tween in the house dealing with sneaky clogged pores, or perhaps they're a fan of face painting adventures, then you're about to discover a skincare secret that's both practical and fun.</span><br></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Enter the world of oil cleansers! These magical elixirs are like a gentle wave of freshness for the skin. They work wonders by giving those pesky pores a thorough cleansing, making it a super-effective preventive measure against breakouts. Plus, when it's time to wash off that artistic face paint masterpiece, an oil cleanser is your best friend.</span><br></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><span style="color: inherit;">No need for harsh scrubbing – oil cleansers are the superheroes of gentleness. Our top pick? The&nbsp;</span><u><a href="https://koreanskincare.nl/products/pyunkang-yul-deep-cleansing-oil" class="" style="text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(86, 173, 255);" data-position="2">Pyun</a><a href="https://koreanskincare.nl/products/pyunkang-yul-deep-cleansing-oil" class="" style="color: rgb(86, 173, 255);" data-position="2">gkang Yul Deep Cleansing Oil</a></u><span style="color: inherit;">. It's not only super effective at cleansing but also incredibly kind to the skin.</span></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Here's the best technique: Apply the oil cleanser using light, soothing circular motions. Remember, be extra gentle, especially around those delicate under-eye areas. Enjoy a luxurious 1–3 minute massage, add a smidge of water, and continue with the gentle caresses for another 30 seconds to a minute. Finish off with a refreshing rinse of lukewarm water.&nbsp;</span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921306" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1681731921306"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang