 gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-5051" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">4. Pyunkang Yul - Kids & Baby Face Lotion</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1680167918241" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1680167918241"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p>When it comes to skincare routines for tweens and teenagers, it's important to understand that different skin types have different needs. While some individuals with oily skin may find enough moisture from using a toner alone, those with dry or combination skin should consider incorporating a moisturizer into their daily regimen for the best results.</p><p><br></p><p>Moisturizers play a crucial role in skincare by providing essential hydration to the skin and helping to retain moisture. Beyond that, they offer additional benefits such as soothing the skin and bolstering its natural barrier.&nbsp;</p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">By applying a moisturizer, you not only replenish moisture lost throughout the day but also create a protective shield that seals in the benefits of previously applied toners, serums, or essences. This step is vital in ensuring that your skin remains radiant, healthy, and resilient.</span><br></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p>Our pick on top tween and teen moisturizer is the <a href="https://koreanskincare.nl/products/pyunkang-yul-kids-baby-face-lotion" class="" data-position="8"><u style="color: rgb(86, 173, 255);">Pyunkang Yul Kids & Baby Face Lotion</u></a>. This lotions' consistency is not too thick or thin on the skin when applying, making them suitable for multiple skin types. This one has our vote, because of its clean ingredients, it is minimalistic and also it family safe label.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1680167685730" data-id="1680167685730"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1680167918202" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1680167918202" data-assigned-ver="4" style="min-height: auto;"><div class="module" data-variant="33188526882879" style="" data-current-variant="40081807245375">{% assign product = all_products['pyunkang-yul-kids-baby-face-lotion'] %}{% unless product.empty?  %}{% form 'product', product, id: "", class: "AddToCartForm ", data-productid: product.id %}<input name="id" type="hidden" value="{{product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id}}" data-produ